	<h1 class="title">美克美家也要做家居买手店，但光卖“讲究”还是不够</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-30 15:16:09 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/12829/medium/12829.jpg?1438236140" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="12829" data-title="《美克美家也要做家居买手店，但光卖“讲究”还是不够》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12829/medium/12829.jpg?1438236140" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12829.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
